<p><strong>SHIPPING TIME:</strong><br>Most orders are shipped next business day.&nbsp; You will receive an email if there is any delay in the shipping of your order.&nbsp; Made-To-Order products will be shipped with a delay of 3 days. &nbsp;On the average orders take 4 to 5 working days to arrive once shipped.</p><p><strong>SHIPPING ADDRESS:</strong><br>WORSHIP WARRIORS <u>does not</u> ship to PO Boxes. &nbsp;A physical shipping address is required by our shipping carriers to deliver packages.</p><p><strong>SHIPPING CARRIERS:</strong><br><img src="https://worshipwarriors.net/images/icons/t_ups-logo2.jpg"></p><p>WORSHIP WARRIORS main postal carrier is the United Postal Service (UPS) to ship packages. &nbsp;We occasionally ship with the United States Postal Service. Shipping is during normal business hours (EST), Monday-Friday&nbsp;(no holidays).&nbsp; If you would like more information<strong>&nbsp;How We Process Orders</strong>&nbsp;see the <a href="https://worshipwarriors.net/index.php?main_page=conditions">CONDITIONS OF USE PAGE</a>.</p><p><strong>INTERNATIONAL SHIPPING:</strong><span style="color:#ff0000;">&nbsp;</span><br><span style="color:#ff0000;"><strong>REQUEST ONLY</strong></span></p><p><span style="color:hsl(0, 0%, 0%);">It is best to check and see if your country has taxes on incoming shipments. &nbsp;Shipping can be very expensive, and country vat taxes would be added once the shipment leaves the US. &nbsp;We do not have information on what country taxes are involved after a shipment leaves the USA.</span></p><p><img src="https://worshipwarriors.net/images/t8_blue-globe.jpg" alt="We are an INTERNATIONAL SHIPPER" width="75" height="50"></p><p><strong>ORDER STATUS:</strong><br>An itemized packing slip is sent with every order. You can check your <a href="https://worshipwarriors.net/index.php?main_page=order_status">Order Status</a>&nbsp;at anytime to see your purchasing history with WORSHIP WARRIORS.</p><p><strong>LOW STOCK ITEMS:</strong><br>Occasionally, our inventory may be low on an item&nbsp;in your order. If this happens we will contact you to let you know when you can expect shipment of your order. We can also ship a partial order and items on back-order will ship as soon as inventory is restocked.<strong> Please note:</strong>&nbsp;<i>we are selling out of certain products and will not be reordering them, check for that notification on the products page.</i></p><p><strong>STORE POLICY:</strong><br><span style="color:#ff0000;"><strong>ALL SALES ARE FINAL - NO RETURNS ACCEPTED</strong></span><br>Please <a href="https://worshipwarriors.net/index.php?main_page=contact_us">contact Lora</a> for any questions about our returns policy.</p><p><img src="https://worshipwarriors.net/images/h3bg.gif"></p><p><img src="https://worshipwarriors.net/images/bullet.gif"> Please Read Our -&nbsp;<a href="https://worshipwarriors.net/index.php?main_page=privacy">PRIVACY NOTICE</a></p>